*{{cite book|title=Six Red Months in Russia: An Observer's Account of Russia Before and During the Proletarian Dictatorship|url=http://digital.library.upenn.edu/women/bryant/russia/russia.html|publisher=George H. Doran Company|location=New York|year=1918|oclc=464606065}}

